\b0 \cf0 QTCoreVideo102 is a Cocoa application demonstrating how to render a QuickTime Movie using OpenGL and the Core Video texture pipeline.\
\
This application is the first in a series of applications demonstrating the synergy between QTKit, CoreVideo, and OpenGL.\
\
QTCoreVideo102 advances the QTCoreVideo101 sample by introducing several reusable classes that make working with QuickTime Visual Context rendering and OpenGL Views easier and more flexible.\
\
